de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag

Class BibliothecaTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.BaseTag
      • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.ISO15693Tag
        • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.BibliothecaTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BaseTag>

    public class BibliothecaTag
extends ISO15693Tag
    Class extends the ISO 15693 RFID tag with the Bibliotheca specific data model, which is based in the default DDM (Daenisches Daten Model) model. Communication is based on the Feig IscTagHandler API. Instances of this class support XML serializing by JAXB.
